user.biography: I think you're pretty cool. Content Creator for @guildesports Business Inquiries Managed by InterTalent

node.text:
AD | I got invited by @Cineworld and @Disney to go to the film premiere of #FreeGuy, the new open world gaming movie with @vancityreynolds. It was super fun and the film was so wholesome! If you’re into your gaming, you’re gonna love this! On top of this, I am going to feature on a Cineworld promotional video which you’ll be able to watch on their channels.
I got to watch it on a Cineworld Superscreen which was an amazing experience. I definitely recommend it! The screen was huge and the sound was so crisp.
If you want to check the film out yourself on a Superscreen, or another special format screen including @IMAX or @4DXglobal, make sure you book your tickets on @Cineworld’s website via the link in my bio. #CineworldSuperscreen
